short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make Chat-GPT a teammate in your Google Meet and Zoom calls

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
- Add ChatGPT to your video calls (Zoom & Google Meet) 
- Be part of the same ChatGPT conversation with the other call members (multiplayer mode)  

Bring Your Own Key:
In order to minimize subscription costs and allow users to only pay for their own queries, Meet-GPT requires users to provide and use their own OpenAI API keys. These keys are stored in the user's browser and are never send or shared with anyone else.
